  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下总部和场地的IP规划，现在网络越来越复杂了。我想用思维导图的形式呈现，从根节点开始叫\"Piano IP - Sede + Campo\"，这样能一目了然。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Piano IP - Sede + Campo",
        "root"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，根节点是IP规划的总览，涵盖总部和场地两个主要部分。那第一层分支您希望怎么划分？是按地理位置还是按功能域？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Piano IP - Sede + Campo",
        "root"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "按地理位置分更清晰。第一层放\"Sede (10.10.0.0/16)\"作为总部的大段，另外还有一个\"VPN Remoti\"分支给远程接入的设备。这样物理位置和逻辑接入方式就分开了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sede (10.10.0.0/16)",
        "VPN Remoti"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以第一层两个主要分支：总部用10.10.0.0/16这个B段，VPN远程接入单独列出来。那总部下面需要展开哪些VLAN？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sede (10.10.0.0/16)",
        "VPN Remoti"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "总部下面有六个VLAN。第一个是VLAN10做票务系统，网段是10.10.10.0/24，我们叫\"VLAN10 Ticketing\"。这是售票窗口和后台用的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VLAN10 Ticketing (10.10.10.0/24)",
        "Sede (10.10.0.0/16)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加VLAN10 Ticketing节点，挂载在总部下面。继续下一个？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VLAN10 Ticketing (10.10.10.0/24)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "然后是VLAN20，专门跑视频流量，主要是监控系统的骨干传输，网段10.10.20.0/24，标注为\"VLAN20 Video\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VLAN20 Video (10.10.20.0/24)",
        "Sede (10.10.0.0/16)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "VLAN20 Video已添加。视频流量独立VLAN是明智的，避免和其他业务争抢带宽。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VLAN20 Video (10.10.20.0/24)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来是VLAN30，IoT设备专用，10.10.30.0/24。我们标注成\"VLAN30 IoT\"，门禁、传感器这些不太可信的设备都扔这里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VLAN30 IoT (10.10.30.0/24)",
        "Sede (10.10.0.0/16)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "VLAN30 IoT已记录。我注意到您用了\"VLAN30\"这个名称，后面VPN那边也有设备类型，需要保持命名风格一致吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VLAN30 IoT (10.10.30.0/24)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "总部这边保持VLAN编号命名，VPN那边按功能命名，场景不同。继续，VLAN40是管理网，10.10.40.0/24，\"VLAN40 Mgmt\"，交换机、防火墙的管理地址都在这。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VLAN40 Mgmt (10.10.40.0/24)",
        "Sede (10.10.0.0/16)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "VLAN40 Mgmt已添加。管理网独立出来，符合安全最佳实践。还有两个VLAN？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VLAN40 Mgmt (10.10.40.0/24)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，VLAN50给员工无线，10.10.50.0/24，\"VLAN50 WiFi Staff\"。VLAN60是DMZ，10.10.60.0/24，放对外服务的服务器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VLAN50 WiFi Staff (10.10.50.0/24)",
        "VLAN60 DMZ (10.10.60.0/24)",
        "Sede (10.10.0.0/16)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加VLAN50 WiFi Staff和VLAN60 DMZ。总部六个VLAN都齐了：Ticketing、Video、IoT、Mgmt、WiFi Staff、DMZ。现在处理VPN Remoti分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VLAN50 WiFi Staff (10.10.50.0/24)",
        "VLAN60 DMZ (10.10.60.0/24)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，VPN Remoti下面分四类设备。第一类是\"Dispositivi azionabili\"，可远程操作的设备，比如能远程开关的机电设备，网段10.20.10.0/24。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dispositivi azionabili (10.20.10.0/24)",
        "VPN Remoti"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Dispositivi azionabili节点。这类设备安全性要求高，单独网段便于做ACL。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dispositivi azionabili (10.20.10.0/24)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二类是远程监控用的\"Telecamere\"，10.20.20.0/24。这些摄像头通过VPN回传视频到总部的VLAN20。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Telecamere (10.20.20.0/24)",
        "VPN Remoti",
        "VLAN20 Video (10.10.20.0/24)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，Telecamere走VPN回来，流量最终汇聚到总部的VLAN20 Video。这个流向关系我记下了，虽然图上不画连线，但逻辑是通的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Telecamere (10.20.20.0/24)",
        "VLAN20 Video (10.10.20.0/24)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第三类是\"Totem\"，自助服务终端，10.20.30.0/24。分布在各个场地，通过VPN接入中心系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Totem (10.20.30.0/24)",
        "VPN Remoti"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Totem已添加。这类设备用户接触多，安全策略需要特别留意。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Totem (10.20.30.0/24)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后一类是\"Staff mobile\"，10.20.40.0/24，给移动办公的员工平板、笔记本用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Staff mobile (10.20.40.0/24)",
        "VPN Remoti"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Staff mobile已添加。VPN Remoti四个子项全部完成：Dispositivi azionabili、Telecamere、Totem、Staff mobile。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Staff mobile (10.20.40.0/24)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说的VLAN30 IoT，你写的是\"VLAN30 IoT\"对吧？我需要确认一下，因为后面我可能还会提到vlan30这个关键词做交叉引用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VLAN30 IoT (10.10.30.0/24)",
        "vlan30"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，节点名称是\"VLAN30 IoT (10.10.30.0/24)\"。您提到的vlan30作为关键词，我会记住它指向这个IoT网段。需要调整显示方式吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VLAN30 IoT (10.10.30.0/24)",
        "vlan30"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 25,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不用调整，这样就行。整个结构我再看一遍：根节点是Piano IP - Sede + Campo，下面分Sede (10.10.0.0/16)和VPN Remoti两大块，六个VLAN加四类远程设备，IP规划清晰多了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Piano IP - Sede + Campo",
        "Sede (10.10.0.0/16)",
